These TIFF fixture files are sourced from:

  https://github.com/developmentseed/async-tiff
  (MIT license, fixtures under libtiff permissive license)

The original libtiff COPYRIGHT is included alongside these files.

Only the specific fixtures used by Rasteret's test suite are included here:

  tiled-oversize-gray-i8.tif   LZW + predictor=2, oversized tile
  tiled-rgb-u8.tif             Tiled RGB, header parser tests
  predictor-3-gray-f32.tif     Float predictor=3 (stripped)
  int16_zstd.tif               ZSTD int16 (stripped)
  issue_69_lzw.tiff            LZW uint16 regression fixture
  random-fp16-pred2.tiff       Float16 + integer predictor
  random-fp16-pred3.tiff       Float16 + float predictor
  bigtiff/BigTIFF.tif          BigTIFF endianness test
  bigtiff/BigTIFFLong.tif      BigTIFF endianness test
  bigtiff/BigTIFFMotorola.tif  BigTIFF endianness test (big-endian)
